{"tid":1722081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【警世必讀】攻擊大學、懲教代警都係局，目的係要選舉前大濫捕，民主派選民冇得投票！","createTime":"2019-11-14T21:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T03:45:49.000Z","uid":201027,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e2668b4a26249930238278e01673fe89fef32b2b","tid":1722081,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:59:00.000Z","msg":"(借account)<br />\n<br />\n前幾日警察強攻中大，令好多前線勇武返晒學幫拖，更令好多支援前線嘅市民同補給人去晒中大。<br />\n<br />\n然後尋日就開始搞其他學校，但全部都無強攻入去，只喺外圍嚇你，<ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">目的係要所有勇武前線返學校保衛校園，變相困咗一班最激進嘅喺學校範圍</span></ins>。所以呢兩日喺剩低堵路同快閃都係二等兵或遊離份子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兵力不足，港共就出動福建幫同鄉黑對付出面班人，目的係<ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">聲東撃西，一網打盡</span></ins>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人中晒計！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重有24號區選一定唔取消，<ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">23號一定出現最強烈嘅濫捕，令到泛民無人投佢哋票</span></ins>！<br />\n<br />\n點解政府要向懲教借兵，唔係叫佢哋出去拉人，而係叫懲教代替警隊守住狗屋，而放晒真黑警、武警、公安上街濫捕！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好自為之！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a6633196c31724c344f987d6a65782d3fa8f60","tid":1722081,"uid":33985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T23:01:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6e25d59763eec26205e89121e9bcc41a5510565","tid":1722081,"uid":212623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T23:03:19.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"1ac8aee1f9e24ec056074c749fc5fe3d967b7c44","tid":1722081,"uid":318817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:23:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97e79e930cc72ab8c138242ef9282c9648e89dff","tid":1722081,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:45:16.000Z","msg":"大佬呀 你望下個投票人數先講野啦<br />\n行動日開埋呢啲post都唔知做咩"},{"pid":"4fcc838366b3b116a878bc22a622642ed9c82321","tid":1722081,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}